''See also [[comma]]''
==English==

===Pronunciation===
*/kō'mə/, /ˈkəʊmə/, /"k@Um@/

===Etymology 1===
From {{Gr.}} [[κωμα]], “deep sleep”

====Noun====
'''coma''' ([[comas]])
#A state of sleep from which one may not wake up, usually induced by some form of trauma.

====Translations====
{{top}}
