*Finnish: [[kooma]], [[tajuttomuus]]
*German: [[Koma]] {{n}}
*Greek: [[κώμα]] [ˈko̞ma] {{n}}, [[λήθαργος]] [ˈliθarˌɣo̞s] (means "deep sleep" but it's better translated as "lethargy") {{m}}
{{mid}}
