*Polish: [[śpiączka]] {{f}}
*[[Slovak]]: [[bezvedomie]] {{n}}, [[kóma]] {{f}}
*Swedish: [[koma]]
{{bottom}}

===Etymology 2===
From {{L.}} [[coma#Latin|coma]], “hair of the head”; from {{Gr.}} [[κόμη]]

====Noun====
'''coma''' ([[comas]])
#{{astronomy}} A cloud of dust surrounding the nucleus of a comet.
